,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:01:30.000Z","msg":"租呢d究竟賺唔賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80102a66df798d4f7ce4c384f0b07203c51e825","tid":14083,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:04:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>租呢d究竟賺唔賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔旨在賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等間鋪無咁寡"},{"pid":"b5c896cab656ad43767f69d922a2083968891631","tid":14083,"uid":4855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>租呢d究竟賺唔賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔旨在賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等間鋪無咁寡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前做過<br />\n我間舖同人夾 其實志在有個位收工落去吹下水<br />\n<br />\n你預算開個價都有吸引力既<br />\n但我以前就fd搭fd問人租唔租<br />\n其實有一半格都係自己友冇倉租收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409cebe1cff1e440c3e0b53776775575ff69fbce","tid":14083,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>租呢d究竟賺唔賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔旨在賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等間鋪無咁寡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前做過<br />\n我間舖同人夾 其實志在有個位收工落去吹下水<br />\n<br />\n你預算開個價都有吸引力既<br />\n但我以前就fd搭fd問人租唔租<br />\n其實有一半格都係自己友冇倉租收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁諗<br />\n個價我諗住開~150-250<br />\n問題係 我用咩途徑可以搵到人黎租？<br />\nIg 我岩岩開左 但唔知點宣傳"},{"pid":"2b90b8fafa65bab3fcfb4c405d1004f81f5de88f","tid":14083,"uid":22484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:14:33.000Z","msg":"有啲興趣 location?"},{"pid":"36c6f30d5981ee73950f8404e28cb51f0691f5c5","tid":14083,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲興趣 location?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鰂魚涌"},{"pid":"6e1b50f333006eee540259372f99789e48a17006","tid":14083,"uid":1660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>租呢d究竟賺唔賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔旨在賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等間鋪無咁寡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前做過<br />\n我間舖同人夾 其實志在有個位收工落去吹下水<br />\n<br />\n你預算開個價都有吸引力既<br />\n但我以前就fd搭fd問人租唔租<br />\n其實有一半格都係自己友冇倉租收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁諗<br />\n個價我諗住開~150-250<br />\n問題係 我用咩途徑可以搵到人黎租？<br />\nIg 我岩岩開左 但唔知點宣傳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我意思問 租呢d既人會放d咩落去賣，有無人會去買，怕唔怕比人偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45558d063134708c4129e727dc3ee568e21c72df","tid":14083,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我係做放租個個<br />\n但唔知咩途徑搵人租</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有意<br />\n點搵你"},{"pid":"d043f8d113fedc2d962c9925461928065205ec24","tid":14083,"uid":4855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>租呢d究竟賺唔賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔旨在賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等間鋪無咁寡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前做過<br />\n我間舖同人夾 其實志在有個位收工落去吹下水<br />\n<br />\n你預算開個價都有吸引力既<br />\n但我以前就fd搭fd問人租唔租<br />\n其實有一半格都係自己友冇倉租收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁諗<br />\n個價我諗住開~150-250<br />\n問題係 我用咩途徑可以搵到人黎租？<br />\nIg 我岩岩開左 但唔知點宣傳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我意思問 租呢d既人會放d咩落去賣，有無人會去買，怕唔怕比人偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前賣毒撚野<br />\n本身舖頭會放d舖主（我地有幾個人）去旅行收集既得意野/二手野<br />\n租既人都係賣毒撚野<br />\n有冇人買好睇你擺乜<br />\n有d格係幾旺 有d回唔到本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n偷就唔會既 我以前幾個人夾 大鎖匙都係兩抽<br />\n咁門口本身又有鎖<br />\n租格人黎到報返number咪開返俾你執位<br />\n唔會直接俾鎖匙佢地"},{"pid":"00e7531d74992befcc04cff0f6d5fb401e44e7b7","tid":14083,"uid":4855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:26:45.000Z","msg":"講多少少 其實d格主甚至乎當個格係保險箱<br />\n<br />\n舉例：<br />\n我係格主 我上lihkg賣緊比卡超公仔<br />\n我住沙頭角 唔通下下約人先再交收咩<br />\n咪放幾隻入格 有人trade就經過執格仔拎完落地鐵交收"},{"pid":"edaacb2b3db4cb4391c5838c30ee417addf91290","tid":14083,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>租呢d究竟賺唔賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔旨在賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等間鋪無咁寡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前做過<br />\n我間舖同人夾 其實志在有個位收工落去吹下水<br />\n<br />\n你預算開個價都有吸引力既<br />\n但我以前就fd搭fd問人租唔租<br />\n其實有一半格都係自己友冇倉租收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁諗<br />\n個價我諗住開~150-250<br />\n問題係 我用咩途徑可以搵到人黎租？<br />\nIg 我岩岩開左 但唔知點宣傳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我意思問 租呢d既人會放d咩落去賣，有無人會去買，怕唔怕比人偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都係宣傳居多<br />\n我見啲人係租一格 放佢啲野 跟住就係佢whatsapp"},{"pid":"16aa9f38ce01361b62fb96f01361a19fe0d24599","tid":14083,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:11:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實我係做放租個個<br />\n但唔知咩途徑搵人租</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有意<br />\n點搵你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEmail? 跟住俾你我whasapp"},{"pid":"589ade25cf1f4a7e323d77232cf1fc689e28a989","tid":14083,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實我係做放租個個<br />\n但唔知咩途徑搵人租</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有意<br />\n點搵你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEmail? 跟住俾你我whasapp</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一係instagram"},{"pid":"b0c0aae7d8a594b56810fd6e0a9b7348e82739d9","tid":14083,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實我係做放租個個<br />\n但唔知咩途徑搵人租</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有意<br />\n點搵你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEmail? 跟住俾你我whasapp</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一係instagram</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMumu_lovefamily"},{"pid":"0418dddfd0c8fee15f040efaf6fadee43d1fb46c","tid":14083,"uid":11045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:26:27.000Z","msg":"租緊一格西九龍，想轉去旺角，但太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1aae4569e44a148f83194d7228ceef1709f303","tid":14083,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:36:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>租緊一格西九龍，想轉去旺角，但太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾錢一個月？"},{"pid":"19fc55390da2e7e4fc5b199109053ca4fe380527","tid":14083,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco