":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有做過間好撚仆街嘅格仔鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲客貨好賣就自己都入埋一份<br />\n有人要買嗰陣就賣番公司貨<br />\n即係個客啲貨同display<span style=\"color: red;\">無分別</span>得個擺字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241dfaace2dba8fd9cb1e41b8979af049b5adc07","tid":14083,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:01:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人流如何?<br />\n主要乜年齡層經過?<br />\n如果~100左右我都有興趣租格賣之前入落既貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然無旺角銅鑼灣咁勁啦<br />\n我見就師奶多 有時都有情侶<br />\n學生反而無乜點見過"},{"pid":"11067203437f30609e81a2544723116e8e59e757","tid":14083,"uid":52096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"你ig個電話係唔係無whatsapp ？"},{"pid":"a9992684e753394f74927ab0468b9afdd29cf1f0","tid":14083,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你ig個電話係唔係無whatsapp ？</blockquote><br />\n打錯左原來 而家可以了"},{"pid":"508374be0db8f2d80ca69f3048889eed30fbd550","tid":14083,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有做過間好撚仆街嘅格仔鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲客貨好賣就自己都入埋一份<br />\n有人要買嗰陣就賣番公司貨<br />\n即係個客啲貨同display得個擺字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下點搵人黎租？"},{"pid":"e6e11c92ff025003e64103f2b97d2d3c8ba17114","tid":14083,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco