都入埋一份<br />\n有人要買嗰陣就賣番公司貨<br />\n即係個客啲貨同display得個擺字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問下點搵人黎租？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好睇個商場嘅人流喎<br />\n人流多嘅自自然然會有人入黎租<br />\n<br />\n我嗰陣番嗰間window display $2500一個月都有人自己走入黎租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見萬利巴打個間係地牢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n旺角都有啲格仔鋪係地牢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}